Class APILocator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dotmarketing.business.Locator<com.dotmarketing.business.APIIndex>

  • public class APILocator
extends Locator<com.dotmarketing.business.APIIndex>
    APILocator is a factory method (pattern) to get single(ton) service objects. This is a kind of implementation, and there may be others.
